v2: referee's comments incorporated; proof of Prop. 2.4 corrected;
  note that in the non-radial case Prop. 2.4 and Theorem 1.1 (i) is restricted
  to s>1/4

inverse Cartan coefficients for E_7 in Figures 1, 2 and 3 corrected;
  related mistake in the marking scheme for diagrams of type E_n corrected;
  many minor corrections and clarifications; more examples
